data.Generated_facility_notes_full_text: The state does not provide facility-level data.
data.Public_Notes: New Hampshire reports long-term care COVID-19 data for Long-Term-Care Settings. New Hampshire provides cumulative totals for resident and staff cases and resident and staff deaths. COVID Tracking Project puts Long-Term Care Settings in the Lumped or other facilities category. New Hampshire reports cumulative but not outbreak data. NH does not provide facility-level data. New Hampshire reports staff and resident cases and staff and resident deaths as combined.
